{"title":"Feedback Spins Modular T-Handle Wrenches, Packable Kit  & Grip Whip Cassette Tool","link":"https://bikerumor.com/feedback-spins-modular-t-handle-wrenches-packable-kit-grip-whip-cassette-tool/","date":1746540380000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_in-unrolled-tool-wrap-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"(Photo by Rupert Fowler/Mountain Bike Connection)\" /></p>\n<p>This new Modular T-Handle Kit of wrenches could become one of the most sought-after tool offerings in the Feedback Sports catalog, combining their signature portability with a premium feel that will please pro and home bike mechanics alike. They are the latest expansion of Feedback’s professional-level tool offerings that maximize portability… and even offer the possibility of pro-style customization. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Grip Whip cassette removal tool\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip_an-easier-cassette-removal-tool-than-a-chain-whip-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Feedback)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, Feedback also has a new quick-clamping Grip Whip designed to take the hassle out of swapping cassettes, so maybe you’ll forget about floppy chain whips…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of wrenches</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_detail-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo Rupert Fowler/MTBCA)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“The new Modular T-Handle Kit provides an unparalleled combination of portability and functionality in a complete Hex and Torx wrench set. With removable lateral bars, mechanics can mix and match the driver sizes, plus tuck the entire kit into the most compact tool roll available.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>T-handle Tech Details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches, 8mm 10mm detents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_detents-up-close-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>set of 10 modular T-handle wrenches with CNC-machined head and hardened tool interface</li>\n\n\n\n<li>extra machined (3 or 5mm) tool ends to allow for deeper access into tight spaces</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3 detents in each crossbar for T- or L-handle use and adjustable access into restricted locations</li>\n\n\n\n<li>can be disassembled and carried in the included PFAS-free tool roll</li>\n\n\n\n<li>mechanics can also mix-and-match the main wrench and crossbars depending on individual needs</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches, options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_assorted-tools-2048x1229.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>color-coded, knurled aluminum spinning sleeves for faster tightening &amp; loosening</li>\n\n\n\n<li>7 red Hex wrenches in sizes: 2, 2.5, 3, 4, 5, 6, and a combined 8/10mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3 black Torx wrenches in sizes: T10, T25, T30</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tool roll optionally attaches to Feedback Team Edition zip-up traveling mechanic tool kit, or can be hung on standard peg wall systems</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll.webp\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches with tool roll\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll-768x1024.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Rupert-Fowler-for-Mountain-Bike-Connection_tool-roll-1152x1536.webp 1152w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo Rupert Fowler/MTBCA)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches, integration with Team Edition toolkit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches_Team-Edition-toolkit-integration.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Feedback Sports Grip Whip easy cassette removal wrench</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Grip Whip cassette removal tool\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_detail-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“Intuitive and easy to use, the new Grip Whip cassette removal tool makes quick work of any cog removal project. Designed for ambidextrous one-handed operation with an ergonomic, textured rubber handle for comfortable grip, this tool is compatible with all 5-13 speed cogsets from SRAM, Shimano and Campagnolo, including SRAM Transmission.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Grip Whip Tech Details</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>31cm / 12 1/4” overall length chomoly steel construction</li>\n\n\n\n<li>spring-loaded jaws open easily with thumb button, but securely hold teeth for easy cassette removal</li>\n\n\n\n<li>6-tooth contact with KMC X chain links for 5-13 speed cassettes on 10-24T cogs</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SRAM standard or T-type, Shimano &amp; Campagnolo cassette compatibility</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ergonomic two-compound rubber handle with molded diamond grip</li>\n\n\n\n<li>8mm cutout in handle to add extra cassette unlocking leverage with an 8mm hex wrench</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Feedback T-Handles &amp; Grip Whip – Pricing &amp; availability</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of hex &amp; torx wrenches, complete set\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Modular-T-Handle-Kit-of-hex-and-torx-wrenches-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Both the new Feedback Sports Modular T-Handle Kit of wrenches and the new Grip Whip cassette removal tool are available now. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Modular T-Handle Kit sells for $200 /235€ and includes all 10 color-coded hex &amp; torx wrenches, plus the roll-up carrying case. Each of the individual tools is also available separately in case you lose one, although we’ve not yet received separate pricing. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand.webp\" alt=\"Feedback Sports Grip Whip cassette removal tool, thumb button spring-loaded\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Feedback-Sports-Grip-Whip-easy-cassette-removal-wrench_in-hand-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The easy-to-use Grip Whip cassette wrench itself sells for $55 / 57€.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://feedbacksports.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>FeedbackSports.com</em></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/feedback-spins-modular-t-handle-wrenches-packable-kit-grip-whip-cassette-tool/\">Feedback Spins Modular T-Handle Wrenches, Packable Kit  &amp; Grip Whip Cassette Tool </a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"6dec1a3d0087866255e0787a876811b62fbd042b7c38ab5ec1e196ddbb7059a2","category":"Cycling"}